  "title": "Retail Sales Promoter (Woodlands / 6 days / Appliances)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Strive to meet departmental sales targets and objectives</li>\n  <li>Actively promote and demonstrate products at dealer locations</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with assigned Sales Executive to achieve both individual and team sales goals</li>\n  <li>Foster and maintain positive relationships with key outlet stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Manage customer inquiries and resolve complaints effectively</li>\n  <li>Monitor and report competitor activities, pricing strategies, and promotional efforts</li>\n  <li>Ensure proper upkeep of product displays and concept counters</li>\n  <li>Support various departmental initiatives and campaigns</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
